channel.title: WoB - Must see
channel.description:
Hi well WoB is World of Battles. It is a Real time strategy game like age of empires, rise of nations etc.. but its free. It is in its beta stages because it was released on the 4th or 8th of December.
Link: http://www.worldofbattles.com/
you can customize your whole army by there looks, color, weapons and armor ;) more information is on there homepage.
